Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:17.81,中上英下,,0000,0000,0008,,{\blur3}（纽约市 儿童基金会）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:06.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:07.67,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 嘿   - 你们在做什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Hey.     - What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:10.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 规划我们的婚礼   - 真巧 我们也正在做同一件事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Figuring out our wedding plans.     - We were doing the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:12.63,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}耶\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:17.30,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太疯狂了 会场 礼服 喜宴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's really crazy. The hall, the dress, the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:20.89,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我完全不知道会这么贵   - 没错 真的是很贵\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- I had no idea how expensive this stuff was.     - Yeah, it is really pricey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:24.60,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 当我听到价目时 都快发疯了   - 那你们怎么办？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- I freaked when I heard the numbers.    - So, what did you two do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:27.69,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很简单 我想出一些 削减开支的办法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It was simple. I came up with some cost-cutting solutions...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:30.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}列了一张清单 然后摩妮卡就叫我去死\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...wrote out a list and Monica told me to go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:33.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没有什么解决的办法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}There's no way around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你只能接受得花大钱的事实\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Just accept that this is gonna cost a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:40.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我听说婚礼的相关产业 一年营业额为四百亿美元\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I heard that weddings are, like, a $40 billion-a-year industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:43.37,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没错 我大概就贡献了一半\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yeah. And I'm responsible for just, like, half of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:48.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}说真的 这些钱应该有更好的用途\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But really, it does seem like this money could be put to better use.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.59,0:00:49.67,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你是认真的吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:53.17,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是啊 你觉得如果我们 把婚礼的钱捐给慈善机构…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yeah. Now, how would you feel if we gave all the wedding money to charity...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:55.72,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后我们在市政府结婚 如何？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...and we just got married at City Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:59.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我觉得那样会让我更想娶你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I think it would make me wanna marry you even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:04.22,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我得告诉你们 那是绝佳的示爱方式\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, I gotta say, you guys, that's an incredible gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:06.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或许你下次结婚时就可以那么做\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Maybe you do that next time you get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:12.61,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不…下次要在夏威夷的日落时分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}No, no, no. The next time's gonna be Hawaii at sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:14.74,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或许下下一次\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But maybe the time after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.15,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 嘿   - 嘿\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Hey.     - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:01:58.40,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有什么事吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:02:02.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}审核我们申请收养的社福人员要来 所以我们在打扫公寓\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Our adoption social worker is coming by, so we're cleaning the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:04.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}"我们"？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:08.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你明知你不要我帮忙 你不能脚踏两条船\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You know you don't want me to help. You can't have it both ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:12.92,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这个人有权决定 你们能不能领养婴儿吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Hey, is this the person who decides whether or not you get a baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:16.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 她要来看看我们住的地方   - 必须要完美无缺\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Kind of. She's coming to see where we live.     - And it has to go perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:21.01,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果她不喜欢我们 她可以不接受我们的美国领养申请\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If she doesn't like us, she can keep us off every adoption list in the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或许我应该过来露个面 她可能是我的连续剧迷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Hey, maybe I should stop by. She could be a soap-opera fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:28.02,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}小人物能够认识大明星 会很令人印象深刻的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's very impressive when the little people know a celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:30.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}"小人物"？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}"Little people"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.31,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}"大明星"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}"Celebrity."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想我整理好这里了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So I think I'm just about done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:40.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}除非你在某处藏了不好的东西 像是色情杂志或香烟？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Unless you have any bad stuff hidden somewhere, like porn or cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:42.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 当然没有   - 钱德\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- No.     - Chandler.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:52.54,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没有藏 而且我被你的影射冒犯了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I don't, and I'm offended by the insinuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:55.34,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好 所以沙发底下没有色情杂志\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So there's not a magazine under the couch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.51,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}马桶水箱后也没有 用胶带黏住的香烟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...or a pack of cigarettes taped to the back of the toilet tank...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:01.22,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或者录影机里的下流录影带？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...or a filthy video in the VCR?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:04.09,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我承认香烟和杂志\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'll admit to the cigarettes and the magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.85,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是录影带不是我的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But that tape is not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:10.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 也不是我的   - 我猜我们永远不会知道是谁的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- It isn't mine.     - I guess we'll never know whose it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 有我可以效劳的地方吗？ - 是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- May I help you?     - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:22.61,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们是来捐一笔 相当大的款项给小孩们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're here to make a rather sizable donation to the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.41,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不论是大或小的捐款 我们都很感激\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, any contribution, large or small, is appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:28.70,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想这笔会让你感激得屁滚尿流\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, I think you're gonna appreciate the crap out of this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:32.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 非常慷慨   - 我们不想被表扬\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Well, this is very generous.     - And we don't want any recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:34.17,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}请匿名处理\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This is completely anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.92,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}匿名处理 来自两位仁慈的陌生人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Completely anonymous. From two kind strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.09,0:03:40.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}张三先生和菲比布非\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Mr. X and Phoebe Buffay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.26,0:03:43.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们可以把你们的名字 放在我们的刊物上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We can put your names in our newsletter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:46.26,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 不需要   - 布非是布料的布 非常的非\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Not necessary.     - Buffay is spelled B-U-F-F-A-Y.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:51.52,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}张三是"麦克汉尼根"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And X is spelled, uh, "Mike Hannigan."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:55.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我代表孩子们非常感谢两位\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}All right, well, on behalf of the children, thank you both very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:59.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 很高兴我们这么做 感觉真好   - 没错 感觉真好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Sure. I'm glad we did this. It feels so good.     - It does. It feels really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.61,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你看 我们得到免费的T恤\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, look. And we get these free T-shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:06.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其实那是我上健身房穿的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Actually, that's the shirt I wore to the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.99,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}难怪湿湿的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's moist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:13.83,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你好 艾玛很快就会醒来的   - 很好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Emma will be up in a minute.     - Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:18.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}罗斯 我听说了你和查莉的事 我很遗憾\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, hey, Ross, listen. I heard about you and Charlie. I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:22.80,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没关系 我相信 漂亮的古生物学家多的是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Aw, that's okay. I'm sure there are tons of other beautiful paleontologists out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.76,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 没错   - 她是绝无仅有的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Absolutely.     - There was one. She's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:29.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其他的看起来都像是 应该去住在桥下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}All the rest look like they should live under a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.27,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你今天打算要做什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So, uh, what are you gonna do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:35.89,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想说带艾玛去游乐场\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, I was thinking of taking Emma to the playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.61,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的天 什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, my God. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:44.78,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我刚刚说的是 我想带艾玛 去上刀山下油锅博物馆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Like I said, I was thinking of taking Emma to the Museum of Knives and Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:53.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}听着 罗斯 我不希望艾玛去游乐场\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Okay, look, Ross. I do not want Emma going to the playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Because?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:05:01.38,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧 如果你真的想知道 我有心理创伤…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}All right, if you must know, I had a traumatic...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:05.17,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我小时候曾经有过秋千意外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...swing incident when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.01,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 真的吗？ - 是的 我当时四岁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Seriously?     - Yes. I was 4 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:10.01,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我坐在秋千上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And I was on the swing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:14.02,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}接着突然间我的头发被链条缠住了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...and then all of a sudden my hair got tangled in the chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:20.77,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}为了要把我救下来 我妈妈必须剪掉一大撮我的头发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And to get me out, my mom had to cut a big chunk of my hair.
