Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:45.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们已经用丰盛的食物 和温暖的衣服宠坏孩子们了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We've really been spoiling the children, what with all the food and warm clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.68,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这么说不公平 一个人的婚礼是很重要的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's not fair. A person's wedding is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:51.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对我尤其重要\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And especially to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:55.44,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我没举行过毕业派对 也没去过毕业舞会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Okay, I didn't have a graduation party. And I didn't go to prom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:59.36,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的甜蜜十六岁 在轮胎场被追着跑\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And I spent my sweet 16 being chased around a tire yard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:03.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}追我的是个精神病息者 口中念着…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...by an escaped mental patient who, in his own words, wanted to:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}"无论如何杀了我"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}"Kill me, or whatever."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:09.58,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以我应该要有个真正的庆典\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So I deserve a real celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:14.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且我才不会让一个 满身大汗的小男人使我觉得内疚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And I'm not gonna let some sweaty little man make me feel badly about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:21.26,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她不是在指你和我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}She could've been talking about either one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:30.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗨 我是罗拉 我是来做领养面谈的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Hi, I'm Laura. I'm here for your adoption interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:33.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你好 我是摩妮卡 这位是钱德\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Hi, I'm Monica. And this is Chandler.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:35.56,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 请进   - 谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Hi. Thank you.     - Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:38.78,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你要不要喝点什么？ - 喝水好了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Would you like something to drink?     - Water would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:41.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们很高兴你来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're so glad that you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.91,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们对展开审核程序感到兴奋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're really excited about getting this process started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:47.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为我们很爱小孩 爱死他们了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Because we love kids. Love them to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:50.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不是真的要他们死 那只是比喻的说法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, not actually to death. That's just a figure of speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们爱小孩的程度…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We love kids the appropriate amount...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在法律规定的范围内\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...as allowed by law.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:01.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你们这里很不错   - 谢谢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Your place is just lovely.     - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:05.30,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是啊 这里有健康家庭的成觉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yes, this building does have a wholesome, family feel to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.76,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我觉得我好像来过这里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I feel like I've been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.93,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这栋公寓还有别的夫妇收养小孩吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Are any other couples in the building adopting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.93,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你是说一楼的那对夫妻吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Is that that couple on the first floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们应该比他们早领养到婴儿的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Because we should get a baby before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:16.52,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那个家伙曾想要卖毒品给我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That guy tried to sell me drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:21.61,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是除此之外 非常健康的公寓\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But other than that, wholesome, wholesome building.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:23.86,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}喔\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:27.53,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 怎么了？ - 我想起来为何我记得这里了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- What?     - I just realized why I remember this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.87,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 是吗 为什么？ - 没什么\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Really? What is it?     - Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:34.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我和住在这栋公寓的一个家伙约会 结果不是很好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I went on a date with a guy who lived in this building. It didn't end very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:37.46,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}该不会是乔伊崔比亚尼吧？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That wouldn't, by any chance, be Joey Tribbiani?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:40.59,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 是的   - 除了他还有谁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Yes!     - Of course it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:45.76,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们度过一个美好夜晚 隔天早上 他答应要打给我 结果他没打\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We had a great night. In the morning, he promised he'd call and he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那个王八羔子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Rat bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:52.10,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你们不是他的朋友吧？ - 天啊 不是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- So you're not friends with him?     - Oh, God, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:54.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 不…   - 不…绝不\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- No, no, no.     - No. Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:58.52,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 不 不   - 不 不 不\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- No, no, no.     - No, no, no. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.23,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}绝不是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.32,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}抱歉 我不该提的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, I'm sorry I brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:07.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们两位有谁打算要待在家里？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So are either one of you planning on staying at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:12.62,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有人在吗？ 里面有没有人预约大明星？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Hello? Anybody in there order a celebrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.75,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}噢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:17.25,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是谁？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:21.04,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那只是个在走廊闲荡的疯子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's just some crazy guy who roams the halls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:23.09,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不过他对小孩很好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}He's great with kids, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:34.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 罗斯 我的天 你还好吧？ - 狗娘养的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Ross. Oh, my God, are you okay?     - Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.94,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}放轻松 我又没说脏话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, relax. I didn't say the F-word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:46.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}罗斯 我就说吧 秋千很邪恶\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Ross, see, I told you! Those swings are evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.28,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对了 就是这个\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}All right. That is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:51.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这将是艾玛此生最后一次荡秋千\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's the last time Emma is getting on one of those things for her entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:54.87,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不…拜托 不是秋千的错 是我的错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}No, no, no. Okay, it wasn't the swing's fault. It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:58.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}多少也是那个小孩的错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And kind of that kid's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:01.25,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他还在笑 真天真\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Who is still laughing. Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:05.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拜托 我们能不能 在有人受伤前离开这里？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Come on. Can we just get out of here before somebody else gets hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:08.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不 等等 我有个好主意 我要你坐在秋千上…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}No. Okay, okay. Wait. I have an idea. I want you to get on the swing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:11.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后你就会了解没什么好怕的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...and you'll see that there's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:17.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道你在打什么算盘了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I know what this is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:20.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你一直以来都在嫉妒我的头发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You've always been jealous of my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:25.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我想说你已经是个成人了 好吗？你应该克服你无谓的恐惧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I just think you're an adult, okay? And you should get over your silly fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.90,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 好啦…我会试试   - 很好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- All right, fine. I'll do it.     - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:31.11,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 除非你手握蜘蛛   - 在哪？在哪？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- If you hold a spider.     - Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:34.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}除非你手握蜘蛛\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If you hold a spider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.80,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们里面没事吧 是我 乔伊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Guys, is everything okay? It's me, Joey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.47,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}领养\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Adoption!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.51,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}怎么回事？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:56.26,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就如同我刚刚说的 那个疯狂的…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, it's just like I said, that crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}伯特 在走廊游荡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...Bert, roaming the halls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:03.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 没事吧   - 继续游荡 伯特\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Guys?     - Keep on roaming, Bert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:06.32,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们今天不想要疯狂\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We don't want any crazy today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:10.78,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 到底是怎么了？ - 我们稍后再谈 伯特 一切都没事\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- What's going on?     - We'll talk later, Bert. Everything's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:14.07,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}听起来不太妙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Everything doesn't sound fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:16.58,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他自己在外面没事吧？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Is he all right out there by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:20.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}没事的 他有看护照顾 他的哥哥…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, yeah. He has a caretaker. His older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}厄尼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...Ernie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:27.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 芝麻街的伯特和厄尼？ - 这不是说编就可以编出来的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Bert and Ernie?     - You can't make this stuff up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:32.84,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你从来没有告诉我 那个家伙 还有你的甜蜜十六岁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You never told me about that guy and your sweet 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 很抱歉发生那种事   - 已经结束了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- I'm sorry about that.     - Oh, it ended okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的一个朋友枪毙了他\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One of my friends shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:43.23,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}至少你将会有一场像样的婚礼 那是你应得的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, at least you'll get a proper wedding. You really deserve that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:47.23,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是 真的 没什么伴随着我成长\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yeah, I really do. You know, I had nothing growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:52.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}就像那些没有我的捐款的孩子一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Just like the kids I took the money from.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:57.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不…我知道你想要做什么 不要逼我再回去那里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}No. No, no. I see where this is going. Don't make me go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:02.33,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}听着 我不能用这笔钱来办婚礼 它已经被污染了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Look, I can't have a wedding with this money now. It's tainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧 我们把钱捐回去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Fine, we'll give the money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:07.59,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果慈善机构的那个家伙 找我们麻烦…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If that guy at the charity gives us a hard time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:11.05,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我朋友已经很久没有枪毙人了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...my friend hasn't shot anyone in a really long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:16.34,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我觉得这里看来是个 养育小孩的好环境\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I must say this seems like a lovely environment to raise a child in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:19.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你大可检查所有的家具底下…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You are welcome to look under any of the furniture...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:23.14,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为…相信我 你绝不会发现 任何色情杂志或香烟在底下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...because, believe me, you won't find any porn or cigarettes under there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:28.69,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在我们四处看看前 让我确认一下 我是否记下需要的内容\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Before we look around, let me make sure I have everything I need up to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:37.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}何不让我带你瞧瞧婴儿房\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Why don't I show you the baby's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你在做什么？ - 你们不让我进来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- What are you doing?     - You wouldn't let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:46.37,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我以为你们有难   - 我们好得很\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- I thought you were in trouble.     - Well, we're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:48.88,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是你叫我"伯特"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But you called me "Bert."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.55,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那是代表危险的暗号\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's our code word for danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:55.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我们没有暗号   - 没有吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- We don't have a code word.     - We don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.34,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们该有个暗号\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We really should.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:02.60,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}从现在开始 "伯特"就是代表危险的暗号\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}From now on, "Bert" will be our code word for danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:05.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那就是婴儿房\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So that was the baby's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:11.48,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 再来我们应该看哪一间房呢   - 哪里都行 但是沙发后面不行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Uh, what room should we see next?     - Any room that isn't behind this couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:17.03,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有人不懂他的笑话 但我觉得他很风趣\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Some people don't get him, but I think he's really funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:26.83,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我一点都不喜欢那样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I did not care for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:28.92,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你得离开\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:31.71,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你和社福人员上过床 却从没打电话给她\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You slept with our social worker and never called her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.96,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}她到现在还在生气 所以不能让她看到你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}She is still pissed, so she can't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:35.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:41.68,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 又怎样了？ - 我忘了我的球棒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- What?     - I forgot my bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:46.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我的天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:50.73,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我最后一次告诉你 我们不想和你做朋友\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And for the last time, we do not want to be friends with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:55.57,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且我们也不想和你买球棒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And we don't wanna buy your bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:59.07,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你在这里做什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.95,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}伯特…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Bert. Bert. Bert. Bert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:09.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 你们是他的朋友吗？ - 我可以解释\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Are you friends with him?     - I can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:11.42,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}乔伊？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Joey?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:14.09,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}All right. Okay. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:18.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Wow. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:21.18,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你竟然有胆回到这里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You have got some nerve coming back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:25.72,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我不敢相信你竟然从没打给我   - 你说什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- I can't believe you never called me.     - Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:29.98,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你大概不记得我的名字了 便告诉你 我叫乔伊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You probably don't even remember my name. It's Joey, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:34.52,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不用费事告诉我你的名字 因为我记得一清二楚 女士\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And don't bother telling me yours, because I totally remember it, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:39.15,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我等你的电话 等了好几个礼拜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I waited weeks for you to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.41,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我给了你电话号码 你从没打给我\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I gave you my number. You never called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:43.74,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}别想转移话题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Don't try to turn this around on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:47.91,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不是社会福利…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I am not some kind of social work...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:49.62,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可以让你…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...that you can just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:51.25,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}说做就做\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:58.67,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 我很确定给了你电话号码   - 是吗？拜托用脑想一想\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- I'm pretty sure I gave you my number.     - Really? Think about it. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:02.34,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你是个漂亮的女人 既聪明又风趣\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You're a beautiful woman. Smart, funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:05.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们一起共度良宵\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We had a really good time. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:09.06,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果你给了我号码 为什么我会没打给你呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If I had your number, why wouldn't I call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:10.77,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我不知道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.19,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}或许我搞错了 我很抱歉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, maybe I'm wrong. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:20.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在道歉已经太迟了 好吗？你伤了我的心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Hey, too late for apologies. Okay? You broke my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:23.61,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你知道我得和多少女人上床 才能忘掉你吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You know how many women I had to sleep with to get over you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 乔伊 等等   - 不\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Joey, wait...     - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:32.25,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我等够久了 我不能再等了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I waited a long time! I can't wait anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:38.67,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}很抱歉让你们目睹这一切 我觉得很难为情\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm sorry that you had to see that. I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:42.05,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 真的没关系   - 我们完全能了解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Oh, that's really okay.     - Yeah. We totally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:45.89,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 约会不容易   - 哇 你们人真好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- Dating is hard.     - Boy, you people are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.43,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我得对你们说…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And I've got to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:53.39,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我觉得你们会是很好的父母\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...I think you're going to make excellent parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.82,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}萝拉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Laura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.20,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们回来了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:10.24,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你们要来拿走更多的钱吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Are you here to take more money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:13.12,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为我想你们要找的是提款机\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Because I think what you're looking for is an ATM.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.00,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不…我们是来把钱捐出来的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}No, no, we're here to give the money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:20.05,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是的 你知道为什么吗？ 为了小孩好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yeah. Because you know what? It's all about the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:22.88,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}虽然也是为了婚礼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Although it's also about the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好吧 拿去 天啊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Ugh. All right, here. No. Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:30.97,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我还没有说的话 先生 恭喜你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If I haven't said so already, sir, congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.23,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好了 你知道吗？够了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Okay, look, enough, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.35,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我得出面干涉 而且我的立场坚定\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I'm stepping in and putting my foot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:38.98,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}身为你未来的丈夫 我要为我们做决定\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}As your future husband, I'm gonna make this decision for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:42.65,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你觉得我们应该怎么做？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}What do you think we should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:46.66,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 已经不是你们可以决定的了   - 什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- It's not your decision anymore.     - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:50.08,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我代表纽约儿童保护协会 拒收你们的钱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}On behalf of the children of New York, I reject your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.83,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}- 但是我们要给你钱   - 我把它还给你们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}- But we're giving you this.     - And I'm giving it back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.00,0:20:56.92,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}接受吧 当作是捐款\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Come on. Consider it a contribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:00.71,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}真是慷慨\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, this is very generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.13,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}拿着支票\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Please, take the check.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:05.59,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}举办一场盛大的婚礼 一起拥有美好的生活\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Go have a great wedding and a wonderful life together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.01,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}听起来不错 我们可以存钱 几年后再回来这里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Sounds good to me. We can save up, come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:10.72,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}捐一笔更大金额的款项   - 没错\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}...and make an even bigger donation.     - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:12.68,中上英下,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当你们回来时 请找布莱恩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And when you do, ask for Brian.
